  "detailed_description": "Escape from an alien spaceship full of secrets. Challenging mashup of old-school action gameplay with puzzle and rhythm elements. Retro CGA inspired colour scheme, bangin' chiptune soundtrack, with enemy movement patterns synced to the beat.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Players must use planning, timing, rhythm, and reactions to survive<br></li><li>Deduce how to disable the security systems and gain your freedom<br></li><li>Find all the hidden stars to unlock the True Ending<br></li><li>Online leaderboards accomodating a wide variety of playstyles<br></li><li>Many challenging achievements to unlock</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103430/extras/aaa4d81bb324d115c437587f316b34c8.poster.avif?t=1612324323\" width=680 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103430/extras/aaa4d81bb324d115c437587f316b34c8.webm?t=1612324323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103430/extras/aaa4d81bb324d115c437587f316b34c8.mp4?t=1612324323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
